11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_NS_FAST_MATH_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_NS_FAST_MATH_H_
13
14#include "api/array_view.h"
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18// Sqrt approximation.
19float SqrtFastApproximation(float f);
20
21// Log base conversion log(x) = log2(x)/log2(e).
22float LogApproximation(float x);
23void LogApproximation(rtc::ArrayView<const float> x, rtc::ArrayView<float> y);
24
25// 2^x approximation.
26float Pow2Approximation(float p);
27
28// x^p approximation.
29float PowApproximation(float x, float p);
30
31// e^x approximation.
32float ExpApproximation(float x);
33void ExpApproximation(rtc::ArrayView<const float> x, rtc::ArrayView<float> y);
34void ExpApproximationSignFlip(rtc::ArrayView<const float> x,
35 rtc::ArrayView<float> y);
36} // namespace webrtc
37
38#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_NS_FAST_MATH_H_
